                     <ul>
                        <li>
                           <strong>Sole Proprietors:</strong> Complete an
                           <strong>end-to-end digital Current Account journey </strong>online through
                           <a href="https://yonobusiness.sbi.bank.in/" target="_blank" class="new_link">yonobusiness.sbi.bank.in</a>.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                           <strong>Other Entities (Partnerships, Companies, etc.):</strong>
                           <br>
                           <ul>
                              <li>
                                 Apply for a current account <strong>online </strong>via yono Business.
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                 Visit a <strong>branch once</strong> to complete the verification process.
                              </li>
                           </ul>
                        </li>
                     </ul>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
