                           <strong>If not registered for digital banking:</strong>
                           <ul>
                              <li> <strong>Sole Proprietors with debit card:</strong>  Register <strong>entirely online</strong> </li>
                              <li>
                                 <strong>Other Business Entities (Partnerships, Companies, etc.): </strong>
                                 <ul>
                                    <li>Initiate <strong> digital onboarding</strong>  for YB / CINB, Trade, or Forex. </li>
                                    <li>Complete the process with a <strong> one-time branch visit.</strong> </li>
                                 </ul>
                              </li>
                              <li>
                                 <strong> Branch-Assisted Onboarding:</strong>
                                 <ul>
                                    <li>Visit any <strong>SBI branch</strong>  to onboard for <strong>YB / CINB, eTrade, and eForex</strong>  in a single visit. </li>
                                 </ul>
                              </li>
                           </ul>
                        </li>
                     </ul>
